~ 
<number box="[509,592,1883,1907]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" value="1.15" valueMax="1.2" valueMin="1.1">1.1–1.2</number>
X long as R 
<number box="[739,747,1897,1911]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45" value="4.0">4</number>
. R 
